WEBVTT

00:01:39.159 --> 00:01:40.519
All-Knowing Manor...

00:01:40.519 --> 00:01:42.000
what kind of place is it exactly?

00:01:42.319 --> 00:01:43.480
Why does everyone want to go there?

00:01:44.239 --> 00:01:44.959
Answering Imperial Grandmother,

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:47.120
I heard that at All-Knowing Manor,

00:01:47.519 --> 00:01:48.879
there is a Treasure of a Thousand Secrets.

00:01:49.319 --> 00:01:50.680
It has implicated many lives.

00:01:51.599 --> 00:01:52.840
I feared further disaster,

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.120
so I sent the Chief of the Court of Revision,

00:01:54.599 --> 00:01:56.359
Hua Qiankun, to go with Ye Li.

00:01:56.480 --> 00:01:57.799
Who is Ye Li?

00:01:58.760 --> 00:02:01.519
Ye Li, son of former Vice Minister of Revenue Ye Zhongming.

00:02:02.319 --> 00:02:04.280
Involved in the Metropolitan Governor's murder case,

00:02:04.519 --> 00:02:06.000
he went to the Manor to redeem himself through service.

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:07.680
And you, Eunuch Li?

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:10.639
I also wish to aid the Empress Dowager and The Emperor.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:12.479
Fearing the Treasure of a Thousand Secrets

00:02:12.479 --> 00:02:14.039
might be used by those with ill intent,

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:17.280
I sent the Secret Inspectorate to investigate.

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:20.599
Don't think I don't know what you are thinking.

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:22.439
The Emperor is critically ill,

00:02:22.439 --> 00:02:23.879
but I am not dead yet.

00:02:24.599 --> 00:02:26.039
You seem rather impatient.

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:28.000
This old servant dares not.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:28.719
Your grandson dares not.

00:02:29.639 --> 00:02:30.840
With The Emperor bedridden,

00:02:31.159 --> 00:02:32.360
we must not fall into chaos.

00:02:34.199 --> 00:02:35.840
If there is progress in this case,

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:37.400
report to me first.

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:39.599
Yes.

00:02:45.439 --> 00:02:47.479
There's nothing here but the river.

00:02:48.479 --> 00:02:50.280
The Red River divides the Manor in two.

00:02:51.039 --> 00:02:52.319
On the south bank, there is only the Ancestral Hall.

00:02:53.159 --> 00:02:54.759
The Manor is surrounded by mountains on three sides,

00:02:55.159 --> 00:02:56.120
and embraces the river on one side.

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:57.680
Protected by miasma,

00:02:58.360 --> 00:02:59.360
it is easy to defend and hard to attack.

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.599
There are no ferry boats by the river either.

00:03:12.159 --> 00:03:12.840
On normal days,

00:03:13.319 --> 00:03:14.479
how do they cross to the south bank?

00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:16.960
The Manor Lord does not wish to disturb the ancestors,

00:03:17.199 --> 00:03:18.280
so except for sacrifices,

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:20.120
boats are not docked here on normal days.

00:03:21.639 --> 00:03:22.199
Ye Li.

00:03:24.719 --> 00:03:25.120
Let's go.

00:03:28.439 --> 00:03:29.159
Look.

00:03:38.080 --> 00:03:40.919
"Gold and jade fill the hall, hidden in deep chambers."

00:03:41.319 --> 00:03:44.039
"Wood carvings and clay sculptures worship mercy."

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:47.479
"Water shimmering, lotus stamens."

00:03:48.719 --> 00:03:50.960
"Candles light the hall, protecting safety."

00:03:52.439 --> 00:03:53.199
This is...

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.759
Metal, Wood, Water, Fire.

00:04:05.080 --> 00:04:06.000
Come, look at this.

00:04:06.439 --> 00:04:08.159
"Gold and jade fill the hall" is the Myriad Treasures Pavilion.

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:10.479
It's in the West Courtyard, belonging to Metal.

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:12.919
"Wood carvings and clay sculptures" is the Main Hall.

00:04:13.199 --> 00:04:14.759
It's in the East Courtyard, belonging to Wood.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:18.240
"Water shimmering" is the Lotus Garden.

00:04:18.759 --> 00:04:19.879
It's in the north, belonging to Water.

00:04:20.519 --> 00:04:22.759
"Candles light the hall" is the south bank's Ancestral Hall.

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:23.879
It belongs to Fire.

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:27.680
If that's the case,

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:30.480
"The immortal points the way to the Book of Longevity."

00:04:31.079 --> 00:04:32.560
The "Book of Longevity" in this line

00:04:35.199 --> 00:04:36.480
refers to the Ancestral Hall.

00:04:40.079 --> 00:04:41.920
The incense in the Ancestral Hall never ceases,

00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:42.839
burning bright every night.

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:45.480
It is the Manor Lord hoping the ancestors can

00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:47.839
bless the Manor with favorable weather

00:04:48.639 --> 00:04:49.639
and everlasting prosperity.

00:04:53.759 --> 00:04:55.160
He's praying for himself

00:04:55.519 --> 00:04:56.600
to have great wealth and honor,

00:04:56.720 --> 00:04:57.560
and to live a long life.

00:04:58.079 --> 00:04:59.959
Then the last line makes sense too.

00:05:00.519 --> 00:05:02.079
"The Book Owner crosses the river, passing the human world."

00:05:02.879 --> 00:05:04.759
This Red River not only divides the Manor,

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:06.120
but also divides Yin and Yang.

00:05:06.639 --> 00:05:07.560
South of the Red River

00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:10.079
are all departed souls.

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:15.920
Since all locations

00:05:16.360 --> 00:05:18.279
are divided according to the Five Elements,

00:05:19.639 --> 00:05:20.439
then Earth...

00:05:25.199 --> 00:05:26.040
is right here.

00:05:26.360 --> 00:05:27.160
The center belongs to Earth.

00:05:33.319 --> 00:05:34.279
We have a tail. Let's go.

00:06:02.199 --> 00:06:04.360
The Manor Lord's room is cleaned daily.

00:06:04.879 --> 00:06:06.040
I also bring people here often.

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:08.680
If there is a Treasure of a Thousand Secrets,

00:06:09.279 --> 00:06:10.399
how would it be hidden?

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:13.600
There must be a mechanism in the room.

00:06:13.959 --> 00:06:14.959
Everyone, split up and look.

00:06:57.040 --> 00:06:57.879
What are you doing?

00:07:00.279 --> 00:07:02.040
Just taking some of Concubine Si's jewelry.

00:07:02.399 --> 00:07:03.279
She won't mind.

00:07:04.120 --> 00:07:05.600
Concubine Si doesn't usually live here.

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:07.199
These were all used by Madam when she was alive.

00:07:07.199 --> 00:07:07.759
Give it to me.

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:08.480
It's fine.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:08.800
Put it back.

00:07:14.439 --> 00:07:15.240
Here, take it back.

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:20.000
We came all this way.

00:07:20.360 --> 00:07:21.439
Didn't make a deal.

00:07:23.079 --> 00:07:24.319
Not even a little reward?

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:25.720
After Madam passed away,

00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:26.920
the Manor Lord missed her dearly.

00:07:27.240 --> 00:07:28.839
He doesn't let anyone touch these things.

00:07:29.360 --> 00:07:31.480
Once, I saw some dust on the dressing table.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:32.560
I wanted to help wipe it off.

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:33.879
But the Manor Lord gave me a good scolding.

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:35.680
Wait.

00:07:49.079 --> 00:07:50.040
There's a groove inside here.

00:07:50.879 --> 00:07:51.879
It looks like a mechanism.

00:07:56.399 --> 00:07:57.160
Try this.

00:07:58.279 --> 00:07:58.920
A Ruyi.

00:07:59.759 --> 00:08:00.480
Where did you get that?

00:08:00.879 --> 00:08:01.680
This belongs to the Manor Lord.

00:08:02.279 --> 00:08:03.120
He has such a noble status.

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:04.759
Why would he wear something so cheap?

00:08:05.079 --> 00:08:05.959
I thought it was strange.

00:08:06.199 --> 00:08:07.759
So I took it off during the autopsy.

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:17.720
It really is the key.

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:48.840
I'll go first.

00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:49.879
Be careful.

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:36.559
Stay close to me.

00:09:56.200 --> 00:09:56.960
Don't be afraid.

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:16.720
This place looks just like the Myriad Treasures Pavilion.

00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:19.639
Could the Treasure of a Thousand Secrets be hidden here?

00:10:25.759 --> 00:10:26.919
Ninth Year of Qingde.

00:10:27.679 --> 00:10:28.720
Tenth Year of Qingde.

00:10:29.360 --> 00:10:30.720
Eleventh Year of Qingde.

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:33.679
These are all arranged by date.

00:10:35.679 --> 00:10:36.559
Tell me,

00:10:36.559 --> 00:10:39.200
if the Treasure of a Thousand Secrets is really hidden here,

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:42.200
then how long will it take us to find it?

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:54.159
If the records are this detailed,

00:10:54.679 --> 00:10:57.519
then there should be archives from the end of the Qingzhi era here.

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:12.960
Found it.

00:11:15.679 --> 00:11:18.120
I followed the petals all the way to the Manor Lord's courtyard.

00:11:18.639 --> 00:11:20.720
They went in and haven't come out since.

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:26.240
Then let's go take a look too.

00:11:39.879 --> 00:11:41.559
News has come from the Palace.

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:43.639
The Palace knows.

00:11:44.600 --> 00:11:45.480
Then what do you plan to do?

00:11:48.759 --> 00:11:50.559
End this quickly.

00:11:52.919 --> 00:11:54.840
The Treason Case of Censor Chao Heng.

00:11:56.399 --> 00:11:57.720
The Treason Case of Censor Chao Heng.

00:12:16.879 --> 00:12:17.559
Ye Li.

00:12:18.519 --> 00:12:19.120
What's wrong?

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:20.600
Come with me.